      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Deliciana</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2014/11/like-he-did/#comment-42114"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2014-11-21T17:27:49-05:00">Friday, November 21, 2014 at 5:27 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Just delicious!  </p>
<p>May I also suggest an old French dish: endive wrapped in plain bold ham (no Proscuitto, no aged artisanal) lapped with Bechamel and gratineed with Gruyere. Rich, creamy, indulgent&#8230;the bitterness of the endive cuts through the fat and salt. Very good on a cold winter night.  Add a green salad with an acidic vinaigrette. Red wine. Enjoy!</p>
    </div>

