    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">nimrodiel</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2014/11/like-he-did/#comment-42135"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2014-11-22T03:54:07-05:00">Saturday, November 22, 2014 at 3:54 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>It&#39;s amazing how the smallest things can bring up memories of a departed loved one.</p>
<p>Last summer I had some particularly pungent cantaloupe and I was hit with a wave of missing my grandfather. my grandpa who had passed away in 1997. My grandfather who would bring us muskmelons fresh from Indiana every summer.</p>
<p>I remembered sitting in my grandparents back yard eating muskmelon with him, the juices running down our chins.</p>
    </div>

