      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Evelien</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2014/11/like-he-did/#comment-42148"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2014-11-25T05:31:01-05:00">Tuesday, November 25, 2014 at 5:31 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>As a Belgian girl I eat endives (&#8220;witloof&#8221;) every week now they&#39;re in season. Did you now there are two kinds of Belgian endives? The ones that are grown in hydroculture (they grow in waterbeds) and the ones that are grown in sand (&#8220;vollegrond&#8221;). It&#39;s the sandy ones you need to look out for, because they&#39;re twice as tasty and intense.</p>
    </div>

