    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>This recipe looks wonderful. And I&#39;m so sorry the three of you are sick! My roommate and boyfriend were both recently sick for 8 WEEKS. It was awful, and I don&#39;t know how I remained impervious to it. Still I sympathize with the both of you! Feel better soon. </p>
